{"tid":565890,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"彩雲國物語將被中國拍成電視劇","createTime":"2018-02-19T12:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T17:16:13.000Z","uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":213,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"4fedbf5175a824905cb17c70c2757fed87de211f","tid":565890,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/20170111/F7Gd-fxzkfvn1634277.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F20170111%2FF7Gd-fxzkfvn1634277.png&h=3e1f6bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n稱席捲亞洲的動畫《彩雲國物語》將被翻拍為中國版真人電視劇，目前該劇已通過備案。從網上公示的備案表上可以看到，電視劇版名稱為《彩雲國》，電視劇將於3月開拍，製作週期12個月，總集數50集。<br />\n<br />\n從人物和劇情簡介上來看，電視劇《彩雲國》 情節和動畫《彩雲國物語》並無太大出入。故事講述了出生於名門「紅」家的紅秀麗雖為嫡長女，卻與父親紅邵可以及父親早年收容的、來歷不明的男子茈靜蘭一起過著貧窮的生活。後面的整個劇情簡述和動畫中的劇情發展基本保持一致。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ylq.com/2017/0112/20170112090448635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ylq.com%2F2017%2F0112%2F20170112090448635.jpg&h=54d16055&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74a83467bca9444e60e4642d929a0241b8fdb4e2","tid":565890,"uid":113178,"like":347,"dislike":4,"score":343,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"乘着風傾聽誰故事"},{"pid":"485140d86d62ea3a7b82dd9ae9bd27df4811c82a","tid":565890,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68581395e0208f20010b359bf7cd8791e5ac3329","tid":565890,"uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T05:43:16.000Z","msg":"幾時有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5542dc3290632bea9b6e516cb50d0f178afbc3d","tid":565890,"uid":48362,"like":104,"dislike":2,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"破壞原作系列 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b4a5c10ca9d8726c5ffad7378e49b1264655fc","tid"